the word opry is a diminutive form of the word opera , coined by broadcaster george d. hay in 1927 as the new name of his program , the wsm barn dance , to demonstrate the realism of folk and country music compared to the theatrics of grand opera .

the grand ole opry : in 2001 , this future celeb " jeopardy ! " contestant got the first opry member award , a replica of the famous mic stand

